config PACKAGE_WPA_SUPPLICANT
	bool"WPA Supplicant for Linux"
	default y
	help
		WPA Supplicant is the IEEE 802.1X/WPA component that is used in the
		client stations. It implements key negotiation with a WPA
		Authenticator and it controls the roaming and IEEE 802.11
		authentication/association of the wlan driver.
